like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"講真，唔好話買唔買污江水，我地其實都應該慳ｄ用水既，老老實實，當你去得多唔同地方旅行，見倒好多人連乾淨水都無啖時，就真係會覺得自己ｄ習慣其實好奢侈，應該應用則用，循環黎用....."},{"pid":"5c3b7ae44b81137e4bf973f084ac6b80f10ec3e9","tid":503703,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"On9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c45de6b16171a5628819769bb3b51359c6ec3c4","tid":503703,"uid":154501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係康城返屋企個陣行過見到呢D野 都好似幾環保 用再造水黎淋花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg&h=2e9b7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg&h=11b6f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾好丫，起碼有心環保下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507da24bf866ded1b229b91c2e3cc453145e66fe","tid":503703,"uid":4064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講好似係簽左約一定要買一定份量<br />\n所以樓主你以依種幼稚園1+1=2思考係完全冇用</blockquote><br />\n只係諗住如果香港人可以珍惜資源既話<br />\n最少唔使俾人成日話要不是大陸，香港早就冇水飲咁姐<br />\n當然唔係話減少浪費就完全解決問題啦，純粹係第一步姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab405ac1681d29f8ba72a45b3e99b49d2a3ac30","tid":503703,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cad5864d67b2a35ed228848cda3c7450d25d0c13","tid":503703,"uid":137726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係康城返屋企個陣行過見到呢D野 都好似幾環保 用再造水黎淋花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg&h=2e9b7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg&h=11b6f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗好多屋苑都應該要有類似嘅嘢, 絕對唔係做唔到, 而係肯唔肯去做</blockquote><br />\n請教巴打，咩叫再造水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bb05920cf6cd1bbc707ac0f3e25a67fef16146","tid":503703,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係康城返屋企個陣行過見到呢D野 都好似幾環保 用再造水黎淋花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg&h=2e9b7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg&h=11b6f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗好多屋苑都應該要有類似嘅嘢, 絕對唔係做唔到, 而係肯唔肯去做</blockquote><br />\n請教巴打，咩叫再造水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屎水掛"},{"pid":"80769a17fa829b0eff1eb00d5d83407720dce4b9","tid":503703,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"批左起化淡廠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27603b690441ed0d8adb5a147ca72b9fcad08af","tid":503703,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你計下每年香港用水量，再假設香港人改變用水習慣，節省到30%用水，睇下唔買污江水夠唔夠用先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如諗下比你用少50%水<br />\n可唔可以唔同支那買水<br />\n<br />\n係唔可以呀!<br />\n而家D食水係多到沖落海<br />\n都要年年比錢支那買水</blockquote><br />\n如果真係每個香港人都開始有節省用水個念頭，係咪最少可以有個誘因去減購買量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果保持呢個用量就算真係起左海水化淡廠都唔會夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要擺脫污江水要多方面配合，而改變生活習慣最少係第一步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你冷靜啲<br />\n而家係人地焗你買咁多，唔係我地問人買幾多<br />\n我就算飲少兩啖汽水佢一樣係倒落海餵魚，呢個係個政府個問題喎<br />\n你搞清楚個方向先"},{"pid":"a33bd412a8477eed88ce3026298a6528d851f255","tid":503703,"uid":163632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係康城返屋企個陣行過見到呢D野 都好似幾環保 用再造水黎淋花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg&h=2e9b7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg&h=11b6f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗好多屋苑都應該要有類似嘅嘢, 絕對唔係做唔到, 而係肯唔肯去做</blockquote><br />\n請教巴打，咩叫再造水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屎水掛</blockquote><br />\n岩岩GOOGLE左<br />\n再造水姐係經過簡單處理既污水 之後唔用黎飲 做其他用途"},{"pid":"b707d1a09040a81964d3469ca71d814194d31838","tid":503703,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"又係例牌將責任推比香港人手法<br />\n幫支那轉移視線<br />\n用買東江水既錢<br />\n同外國買多一倍水都得啊<br />\n浪費你老母"},{"pid":"d723c0015bdcbf3e696cbedf3d81bbed0cc0bfbe","tid":503703,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講好似係簽左約一定要買一定份量<br />\n所以樓主你以依種幼稚園1+1=2思考係完全冇用</blockquote><br />\n只係諗住如果香港人可以珍惜資源既話<br />\n最少唔使俾人成日話要不是大陸，香港早就冇水飲咁姐<br />\n當然唔係話減少浪費就完全解決問題啦，純粹係第一步姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家係焗俾<br />\n不如你提供吓有乜方法叫停港共唔好俾錢支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39ceeeb8f6b7ccb7c78254bad978e5f092fdf8e","tid":503703,"uid":138083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89e876bb5117189f13896fe535ca1995828afd51","tid":503703,"uid":137726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係康城返屋企個陣行過見到呢D野 都好似幾環保 用再造水黎淋花<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F173957_bd306aa9a892bebe9203eb0179d3ee87.jpg&h=2e9b7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F174000_7ec81c3ddf537a53725e7439ad22f306.jpg&h=11b6f4c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗好多屋苑都應該要有類似嘅嘢, 絕對唔係做唔到, 而係肯唔肯去做</blockquote><br />\n請教巴打，咩叫再造水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「再造水」是指經過一連串有效的污水處理及消毒除菌程序淨化的污水，以達到可循環再用之嚴格要求。<br />\n<br />\n再造水的應用範圍廣泛，可用於清洗街道及車輛；灌溉公園及運動場；沖廁、救火及工業用途，以至社區發展及美化工程等。再造水的使用既減少了對環境的污染及自然生態的負荷，亦大大舒緩了對淡水的需求，為持續發展帶來有利因素，並為保護環境作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係乾淨既屎水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係咁既話<br />\n咁要呢D再造水淋花好好喎<br />\n又唔係拎黎飲<br />\n又省到唔少水"},{"pid":"84b6a2f47f61ebe7164ae7fc402ebe111df0a854","tid":503703,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"政府唔出錢搞本地水來源，就算香港人用水減到而家一半都冇得唔用中國臭水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f9a266983356caf6abb5a3967c2d49b419afb9","tid":503703,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"晒9氣啦. 每日百五個慢性同化你地."},{"pid":"028610a6c5b277856ee8a892d265d14b6f0c324e","tid":503703,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"有生之年改變唔到"},{"pid":"4c76d125caf135807ad0bb48d67864fdd68ffb59","tid":503703,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晒9氣啦. 每日百五個慢性同化你地.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你班消極撚, <br />\n一日到黑淨係識話算數,<br />\n明明仲有好多野可以做,<br />\n你一句哂鳩氣就講到唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369af5ddc03f4a82bdf401abb4f82e50b8a1a2bc","tid":503703,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"慳住用係一回事<br />\n買東江水係另一回事<br />\n你幾慳水都要同大陸買<br />\n就算填平幾個水塘都要同大陸買<br />\n同你既生活習慣無關, 唔好拉埋嚟講"},{"pid":"c80fad674b311902a912976554846d7dee2d133d","tid":503703,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你計下每年香港用水量，再假設香港人改變用水習慣，節省到30%用水，睇下唔買污江水夠唔夠用先。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如諗下比你用少50%水<br />\n可唔可以唔同支那買水<br />\n<br />\n係唔可以呀!<br />\n而家D食水係多到沖落海<br />\n都要年年比錢支那買水</blockquote><br />\n如果真係每個香港人都開始有節省用水個念頭，係咪最少可以有個誘因去減購買量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果保持呢個用量就算真係起左海水化淡廠都唔會夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要擺脫污江水要多方面配合，而改變生活習慣最少係第一步</blockquote><br />\n中學畢業未"},{"pid":"7a50b76695376a5bdb05684a9135770e56753308","tid":503703,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"入幾多水，用幾錢入，香港根本無話事權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算淨係比左80%水你，香港都要比返100%既錢<br />\n就連上面缺水香港主動要求減少供應都比廣東省拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為香港人學識慳水就得"}]}